SELECT * FROM "forms" WHERE "slug" = 'my-form' and "forms"."deleted_at" IS NULL LIMIT 1

SELECT "workspaces".*, "user_workspace"."user_id" as "pivot_user_id", "user_workspace"."workspace_id" as "pivot_workspace_id" FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "user_workspace"."user_id" = 53 and "workspaces"."id" = 42 LIMIT 1
SELECT * FROM "form_zapier_webhooks" WHERE "form_zapier_webhooks"."form_id" = 37 and "form_zapier_webhooks"."form_id" IS not NULL and "form_zapier_webhooks"."deleted_at" IS NULL
